body:
@Qilewuqiong tfdbg doesn't support partial runs yet. So currently, to debug partial runs, you can use other debugging tools from tensorflow, including the following
* [tf.Print op](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/Print) See use example at: https://www.quora.com/How-does-the-tf-Print-statement-work-for-TensorFlow
* [tf.add_check_numerics_op](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/add_check_numerics_ops)
